{{year-header}}
== January ==
* '''[[3 January|3]]''' - '''[[J.R.R. Tolkien|John Ronald Reuel Tolkien]] is born to [[Arthur Tolkien|Arthur]] and [[Mabel Suffield|Mabel Tolkien]] at Bank House, Maitland Street, in [[Bloemfontein]], South Africa'''.
* '''[[4 January|4]]''' - [[Arthur Tolkien]] sends a letter to his mother about his new son.
* '''[[31 January|31]]''' - [[J.R.R. Tolkien]] is christened in the Anglican Cathedral in Bloemfontein.

== November ==
* '''[[15 November|15]]''' - Arthur, Mabel, two household servants, and the nurse holding Ronald pose for a picture in the garden at Bank House. The photograph is used in Tolkien Christmas cards sent to family and friends. The image is reproduced in [[J.R.R. Tolkien: A Biography]] and [[The Tolkien Family Album]].
